  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A COSY CO-OP ADVENTURE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the nimble <strong>Squirrel</strong> and the strong <strong>Bear</strong> on a wild journey. Jump, stomp, zoom through colorful cities following <strong>Rascal</strong>'s clues. Travel Europe with your friends and experience <strong>nuttastic</strong> moments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407640/extras/54fad0674681f02725bd7b645353609d.poster.avif?t=1772717341\" width=573 height=185 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407640/extras/54fad0674681f02725bd7b645353609d.webm?t=1772717341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >JUMP, STOMP & MUNCH!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the nimble <strong>Squirrel</strong> and the strong <strong>Bear</strong>. Jump, stomp and munch. Climb famous sights, harvest fruits and nuts. Move trees, trudge through mud or carry giant cakes.<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407640/extras/622fdf81068c37b951d2b20fbcd6949a.poster.avif?t=1772717341\" width=573 height=459 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407640/extras/622fdf81068c37b951d2b20fbcd6949a.webm?t=1772717341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>   </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HAVE YOU SEEN RASCAL?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow the clues and embark on an eventful scavenger hunt with Squirrel and Bear. Rascal, the cheeky badger, placed hints all over Europe. Follow the clues and use the help of your animal friends in each country.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407640/extras/144310216891c84a11070e8956ba2f8b.poster.avif?t=1772717341\" width=573 height=201 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407640/extras/144310216891c84a11070e8956ba2f8b.webm?t=1772717341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DISCOVER THE CULTURES OF EUROPE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take your time to explore each city. Learn foreign languages, eat delicious food, collect souvenirs, participate in traditional customs, dress fashionably and recycle trash. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407640/extras/9fe9572a70cb9fd7749fe047a7372137.poster.avif?t=1772717341\" width=573 height=187 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407640/extras/9fe9572a70cb9fd7749fe047a7372137.webm?t=1772717341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CREATE MEMORIES </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Live in the moment! Gather your friends and family. Grab two controllers. Take photos, document your discoveries and create shared memories!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407640/extras/39fc9186325ebdcf1e4251efb6c175d3.poster.avif?t=1772717341\" width=573 height=187 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407640/extras/39fc9186325ebdcf1e4251efb6c175d3.webm?t=1772717341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >COOPERATIVE PLAY WITH FRIENDS </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let your friends join. Choose between Squirrel and Bear. Combine the strengths of both characters and help each other to succeed on this colorful journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407640/extras/2bb3aefb2bd5178f602a08fcbfeb5f78.poster.avif?t=1772717341\" width=573 height=187 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407640/extras/2bb3aefb2bd5178f602a08fcbfeb5f78.webm?t=1772717341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PACK YOUR BAGS! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel by bus, train, boat, car, tanker, scooter, airplane, tram, or hot air balloon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play comfortably on your couch at home or take Rascal's Escape with you on the go – it's the perfect travel companion for entertainment with new friends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407640/extras/4aa500aa39a87bf32697cbbdde888c56.poster.avif?t=1772717341\" width=573 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407640/extras/4aa500aa39a87bf32697cbbdde888c56.webm?t=1772717341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Made for SteamDeck</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rascal’s Escape</strong> is perfect to bring along on your own journey. Play on the go alone. Or pair your favorite controllers to the SteamDeck to play with friends. Get comfy on the couch and connect your SteamDeck to a TV. SteamDeck and most third-party controllers are fully supported, allowing for a colorful journey anytime and everywhere.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Handcrafted by the Good Evil GmbH.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A COSY CO-OP ADVENTURE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the nimble <strong>Squirrel</strong> and the strong <strong>Bear</strong> on a wild journey. Jump, stomp, zoom through colorful cities following <strong>Rascal</strong>'s clues. Travel Europe with your friends and experience <strong>nuttastic</strong> moments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407640/extras/54fad0674681f02725bd7b645353609d.poster.avif?t=1772717341\" width=573 height=185 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407640/extras/54fad0674681f02725bd7b645353609d.webm?t=1772717341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >JUMP, STOMP & MUNCH!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the nimble <strong>Squirrel</strong> and the strong <strong>Bear</strong>. Jump, stomp and munch. Climb famous sights, harvest fruits and nuts. Move trees, trudge through mud or carry giant cakes.<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407640/extras/622fdf81068c37b951d2b20fbcd6949a.poster.avif?t=1772717341\" width=573 height=459 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407640/extras/622fdf81068c37b951d2b20fbcd6949a.webm?t=1772717341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>   </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HAVE YOU SEEN RASCAL?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow the clues and embark on an eventful scavenger hunt with Squirrel and Bear. Rascal, the cheeky badger, placed hints all over Europe. Follow the clues and use the help of your animal friends in each country.</p><p class=\"bb_pa